# Performance

## GPU compositing

- Add `transform-gpu will-change-transform` (via `GPU_LAYER` from `@/lib/performance`) to:
  - Framer Motion animated elements
  - 3D terminal wrapper and portfolio cards
  - Scroll parallax wrappers (`SectionParallax`, `ParallaxHeading`)
  - Hover glow / custom cursor layers
- Prefer animating `transform` and `opacity` only — never width/height/top/left

## Mobile & 3D

- Disable 3D mouse tracking (`rotateX`/`rotateY`/`perspective`) when `window.innerWidth < 1024`
- Use `useEffect` resize listener for mobile detection in hero
- Skip 3D card stacks on mobile; use flat list layout

## Backdrop blur budget

- **Never** use `backdrop-blur-2xl` or `backdrop-blur-3xl`
- Prefer `backdrop-blur-md` or `backdrop-blur-lg` on section cards and headers
- Keep `.glass-card` CSS blur at 12px max (`blur(12px)`)

## Reduced motion

- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce` via `useReducedMotion()`:
  - Disable Lenis smooth scroll
  - Disable 3D transforms and parallax
  - Replace pulsing PremiumCanvas blobs with static divs
  - Hide custom cursor (`AppSmoothContainer`)

## Background layers

- All PremiumCanvas blobs: `pointer-events-none select-none`
- Decorative gradients and glows must not intercept clicks

## Audio (optional)

- Micro-sounds via `useSound` hook — only after first user interaction (click/keydown)
- Wire through `InteractionProvider` + `Button` onClick

## Build gate

- Run `npm run build` before merging performance changes — zero errors required
